{"tid":542971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇得番工呀！]有巿民稱灣仔沙中綫地盤附近封鎖致未能上班及回家","createTime":"2018-01-28T04:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T06:51:43.000Z","uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"774199d1b5227dc7c7f67028553b19815aebdd7c","tid":542971,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"警方在灣仔沙中綫會展站地盤，處理戰時炸彈，目前正在燃燒炸藥，附近多條行車線需要封閉，警員亦禁止行人前往灣仔碼頭及港灣道體育館一帶。<br />\n<br />\n有住在封鎖範圍內的市民說，警方基於安全理由，禁止他返回住所，但警方未有疏散住宅大廈內的居民，質疑警方的準則。<br />\n<br />\n在封鎖範圍內食肆上班的員工指，自己本來早上7點上班，到現場後獲公司告知回家等待解封再上班，本來以為現場將會很快解封，未有回家，但等候了約5小時仍未解封。<br />\n<br />\n工人昨日在灣仔沙中綫會展站地盤內發現一個戰時空投炸彈，炸彈重約1000磅，內有約500磅炸藥，一旦爆炸，威力可遠至200米。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1377729-20180128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1377729-20180128.htm&d=YgCfX48WJcfWYQB4loxbInIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=cec56cb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1377729-20180128.htm&h=9e69e96c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1377729-20180128.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c93a3d94db10d330693ef7ab2c81f5863ec645c4","tid":542971,"uid":25858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"為了返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba39f711f6ea9ba9eb4fab626040764888fc06c2","tid":542971,"uid":85819,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T04:51:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76b54e85bb7381d9bbf44240a529499b35d7383d","tid":542971,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c93a3d94db10d330693ef7ab2c81f5863ec645c4","tid":542971,"uid":25858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"為了返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T06:17:12.000Z","msg":"香港人嘛"